    ('just-like-me', 0, $$It’s Rahah’s birthday next week. She’s excited about inviting her new friends to her party.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "It’s Rahah’s birthday next week. She’s excited about inviting her new friends to her party.", "bbox": [84.3, 217.0, 407.7, 373.0], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 1, $$“Who will you invite?” asks Mum. “You’ve only been at school a few months. The kids all seem so very different, don’t they?” “No, Mum. I have lots of new friends,” says Rahah.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Who will you invite?” asks Mum. “You’ve only been at school a few months. The kids all seem so very different, don’t they?”", "bbox": [58.8, 75.2, 473.5, 231.2], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“No, Mum. I have lots of new friends,” says Rahah.", "bbox": [58.8, 263.2, 417.1, 335.2], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 2, $$“I want to invite Zerina. She wants to be a ballerina, just like me !”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I want to invite Zerina. She wants to be a ballerina, just like me !”", "bbox": [65.2, 181.5, 402.7, 303.6], "size": 34.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 3, $$“Oh lovely,” says Mum. “Let’s play some dance music then.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Oh lovely,” says Mum. “Let’s play some dance music then.”", "bbox": [37.6, 426.7, 491.1, 498.7], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 4, $$“I hope that Sikelele can come too. He sings in the school choir, just like me .”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“I hope that Sikelele can come too. He sings in the school choir, just like me .”", "bbox": [817.6, 105.0, 1062.6, 308.1], "size": 34.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 5, $$“Oh that’s good - we’ll all have fun singing too.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Oh that’s good - we’ll all have fun singing too.”", "bbox": [58.8, 116.3, 430.1, 188.3], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 6, $$“Can we invite Susheela? She’s got fluffy kittens, just like me .”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Can we invite Susheela? She’s got fluffy kittens, just like me .”", "bbox": [741.6, 165.9, 1048.8, 287.7], "size": 34.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 7, $$“Yes, let’s. She’ll have fun playing with our kittens too.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Yes, let’s. She’ll have fun playing with our kittens too.”", "bbox": [93.5, 226.9, 365.3, 340.9], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 8, $$“And we must invite Yongnam. She loves pink cupcakes even more than I do.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“And we must invite Yongnam. She loves pink cupcakes even more than I do.”", "bbox": [690.9, 73.8, 1077.2, 187.8], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 9, $$“It’s lucky I’m making cupcakes then,” says Mum. “She can have the pink ones.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“It’s lucky I’m making cupcakes then,” says Mum.", "bbox": [65.2, 141.8, 399.4, 213.8], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“She can have the pink ones.”", "bbox": [65.2, 267.9, 427.9, 297.9], "size": 30.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 10, $$“Ah thanks, Mum! I can’t wait.” “Oh Rahah! I’m so excited to meet all your friends. They sound so special - just like you !”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“Ah thanks, Mum! I can’t wait.”", "bbox": [56.7, 92.6, 437.7, 122.6], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Oh Rahah! I’m so excited to meet all your friends. They sound so special - just like you !”", "bbox": [56.7, 176.6, 408.6, 336.6], "size": 34.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 11, $$“But what about you? You love books, don’t you… just like me! Would you like to come to my party too?”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "“But what about you? You love books, don’t you… just like me! Would you like to come to my party too?”", "bbox": [92.1, 170.2, 426.5, 408.2], "size": 31.0}]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 12, $$$$, $$[]$$),
    ('just-like-me', 13, $$TThhaannkk YYoouu!!$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "TThhaannkk YYoouu!!", "bbox": [292.3, 450.8, 351.9, 474.5], "size": 14.2}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 0, $$Khaya lives in Joza township with Gogo Lucy and Mkhulu Majozi. His mother works far away in Cape Town.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Khaya lives in Joza township with Gogo Lucy and Mkhulu Majozi. His mother works far away in Cape Town.", "bbox": [623.6, 96.8, 862.4, 192.8], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 1, $$Every morning, Khaya eats porridge with Gogo on the stoep. The kettle whistles on the paraffin stove. The sun peeks over Joza. “Gogo, tell me a story!” Khaya says.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Every morning, Khaya eats porridge with Gogo on the stoep. The kettle whistles on the paraffin stove. The sun peeks over Joza.", "bbox": [715.6, 181.5, 1041.2, 277.5], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "“Gogo, tell me a story!”", "bbox": [709.7, 313.3, 1022.5, 343.3], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Khaya says.", "bbox": [715.6, 373.5, 808.0, 391.5], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 2, $$Gogo smiles. She tells him stories of rivers and dreams. “K haya,” she says, “when you arebigandstrong, youcanbe anythingyouw ”.tna Khaya smiles and nods.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Gogo smiles. She tells him stories of rivers and dreams.", "bbox": [149.9, 75.3, 417.3, 119.3], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“K haya,” she says, “when you arebigandstrong,", "bbox": [136.7, 159.4, 515.9, 256.9], "size": 19.1}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "youcanbe anythingyouw ”.tna Khaya smiles and nods.", "bbox": [618.5, 249.9, 1088.6, 491.8], "size": 32.6}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 3, $$One Saturday, Mkhulu switches on the TV. Rowers are gliding across the water. “Mkhulu! What are they doing?” Khaya asks. “They are rowing with oars, my boy,” says Mkhulu.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "One Saturday, Mkhulu switches on the TV. Rowers are gliding across the water.", "bbox": [84.9, 120.7, 426.1, 164.7], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Mkhulu! What are they doing?” Khaya asks. “They are rowing with oars, my boy,” says Mkhulu.", "bbox": [624.2, 90.4, 904.6, 261.7], "size": 23.2}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 4, $$Khaya claps his hands. “Oh wow! I want to row too!” He sings, “I want to row a boat, I want to row a boat!”$$, $$[{"role": "SFX", "text": "Khaya claps his hands. “Oh wow! I want to row too!”", "bbox": [792.3, 148.5, 1061.5, 293.9], "size": 34.5}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "He sings, “I want to row a boat, I want to row a boat!”", "bbox": [782.0, 334.5, 1071.4, 427.9], "size": 27.0}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 5, $$Mkhulu sings with him, “Khayawantstorow, Khayawantstorow! Rowaboatwithan oar. Row a boatwithanoar.” Gogo laughs and joins in.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Mkhulu sings with him,", "bbox": [254.6, 62.1, 439.4, 80.1], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Khayawantstorow, Khayawantstorow!", "bbox": [343.1, 118.0, 500.6, 258.3], "size": 22.7}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Rowaboatwithan oar.", "bbox": [645.2, 165.2, 808.6, 270.9], "size": 21.2}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Row a boatwithanoar.” Gogo laughs and joins in.", "bbox": [665.1, 278.4, 1052.8, 464.3], "size": 25.0}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 6, $$From that day, Khaya plays in puddles, draws boats in the sand, and builds toy boats from scraps.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "From that day, Khaya plays in puddles, draws boats in the sand, and builds toy boats from scraps.", "bbox": [85.0, 306.0, 351.6, 376.0], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 7, $$One morning, Mkhulu wakes Khaya early. “Come, Mzukulu, I have a surprise.” Khaya gets ready. Today feels special.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "One morning, Mkhulu wakes Khaya early.", "bbox": [741.9, 168.7, 917.6, 212.7], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“Come, Mzukulu, I have a surprise.”", "bbox": [711.6, 248.5, 947.3, 314.5], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Khaya gets ready. Today feels special.", "bbox": [752.9, 344.7, 906.6, 388.7], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 8, $$They t ake a taxi to Port Alfred. Atthe Kowie River, b oats are lined up.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "They t ake a taxi to Port Alfred.", "bbox": [164.9, 372.6, 411.8, 422.1], "size": 18.8}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Atthe Kowie River, b oats are lined up.", "bbox": [771.8, 144.3, 1080.4, 190.9], "size": 19.6}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 9, $$Rowers are ready with their oars. “Wow, Mkhulu! This is where people row!” Khaya shouts. He watches boats racing fast across the water. He waves at rowers and takes a photo with one.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Rowers are ready with their oars. “Wow, Mkhulu! This is where people row!” Khaya shouts.", "bbox": [85.0, 86.3, 478.1, 130.3], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "He watches boats racing fast across the water. He waves at rowers and takes a photo with one.", "bbox": [652.0, 86.3, 1037.3, 130.3], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 10, $$At the end of the day, Khaya hugs Mkhulu. “Thank you, Mkhulu. You are the best!” “One day, Khaya,” Mkhulu says, “you will row a boat like a champion.”$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "At the end of the day, Khaya hugs Mkhulu.", "bbox": [680.7, 103.8, 1022.2, 121.8], "size": 18.0}, {"role": "SFX", "text": "“Thank you, Mkhulu. You are the best!”", "bbox": [709.9, 157.5, 989.4, 223.5], "size": 30.0}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "“One day, Khaya,” Mkhulu says, “you will row a boat like a champion.”", "bbox": [702.2, 263.8, 999.3, 307.8], "size": 18.0}]$$),
    ('khaya-wants-to-row', 11, $$Khaya smilesandwhispers, Khaya “Khaya wants wantstoroww torow,ro. . Row Row a a boatwithanoar!” boatwithanoar.$$, $$[{"role": "BODY", "text": "Khaya smilesandwhispers,", "bbox": [102.1, 68.8, 314.4, 156.5], "size": 20.9}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Khaya “Khaya wants wantstoroww torow,ro. .", "bbox": [147.3, 199.9, 493.0, 379.1], "size": 36.9}, {"role": "BODY", "text": "Row Row a a boatwithanoar!” boatwithanoar.", "bbox": [751.1, 299.6, 1084.1, 519.9], "size": 37.7}]$$),
